edBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T02:27:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做緊薄餅某傳統公司（果一間）<br />\n，老底47，單錢$3，六日假$8<br />\n你問我答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n洗唔洗入廚房幫手? <br />\n星期六日圍返連單錢大約幾錢個鐘?"},{"pid":"ef935fe2c3462ccd2ef5a55da7c31e71548afcc1","tid":187742,"uid":16636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T05:58:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>係美帝做緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打係美國大？美國邊到做？</blockquote><br />\n東岸<br />\n<br />\n6蚊美金一個鐘+ 最少1蚊美金外賣（越遠越多最多去到5蚊del chg)<br />\n<br />\nTips 全收<br />\n<br />\n我淨係返pt一日大慨4個鐘唔計油700港紙左右</blockquote><br />\n用自己車？<br />\n美國叫外賣係咪好重tips，去過一次叫外賣，個呀叔問我攞toips<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22072d63236e1b1c7203ea77106f323a38eb1824","tid":187742,"uid":37430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T06:04:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>係美帝做緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打係美國大？美國邊到做？</blockquote><br />\n東岸<br />\n<br />\n6蚊美金一個鐘+ 最少1蚊美金外賣（越遠越多最多去到5蚊del chg)<br />\n<br />\nTips 全收<br />\n<br />\n我淨係返pt一日大慨4個鐘唔計油700港紙左右</blockquote><br />\n用自己車？<br />\n美國叫外賣係咪好重tips，去過一次叫外賣，個呀叔問我攞toips<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n要自己車<br />\n<br />\nTips其實正式黎講起碼要15%<br />\n<br />\n我以前叫都冇注意<br />\n<br />\n做落自己辛苦先知多3蚊真係好撚開心<br />\n<br />\n加上我架野係極食油<br />\n<br />\n利申：渣野馬送外賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"463a38eaa963133a0945ae20a02973690bb43f69","tid":187742,"uid":14207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T06:08:46.000Z","msg":"P牌做唔做得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d66a76ecbd8589d2921e997b622ea449ed69f74","tid":187742,"uid":50101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T06:53:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做緊薄餅某傳統公司（果一間）<br />\n，老底47，單錢$3，六日假$8<br />\n你問我答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想當年我做果陣得 $30 粒鐘，仲要冇單錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"111b6680ca44aecaf6df60f1aedc192584707a48","tid":187742,"uid":86865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T07:56:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>做緊薄餅某傳統公司（果一間）<br />\n，老底47，單錢$3，六日假$8<br />\n你問我答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n洗唔洗入廚房幫手? <br />\n星期六日圍返連單錢大約幾錢個鐘?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n全職要，做簡單輕鬆野，例如摺盒，<br />\n星期六日睇你咩鐘數，中午下午一個鐘1-2單<br />\n到夜晚你預一個鐘4-5單"},{"pid":"5ea0388f2e18e4ed5a4404189bf1cc992f8195f0","tid":187742,"uid":86865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T07:58:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>做緊薄餅某傳統公司（果一間）<br />\n，老底47，單錢$3，六日假$8<br />\n你問我答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想當年我做果陣得 $30 粒鐘，仲要冇單錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咩年代，無單錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe5cf03f49ea6925bc66a66bafcc027567c74d07","tid":187742,"uid":16636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T08:39:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>P牌做唔做得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n做得 兩間都見過"},{"pid":"9f3d62b12381cab83e8e27523426ec29f091ea8b","tid":187742,"uid":50101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"