ime":"2017-04-10T17:48:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>做緊薄餅某傳統公司（果一間）<br />\n，老底47，單錢$3，六日假$8<br />\n你問我答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n洗唔洗入廚房幫手? <br />\n星期六日圍返連單錢大約幾錢個鐘?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係其細佬公司 2012全職老底34 單錢3 六日假6<br />\n<br />\n廚房方面整制作唔使 要執食材倉 檢查熱袋咁啦<br />\n<br />\n不過我見好幾個都跳板走去做巴士佬(包括我)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家學緊拖頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3d7412c198c2fd70ae2ebed3b9c41fb8bf028e6","tid":187742,"uid":54058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T17:49:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>做緊薄餅某傳統公司（果一間）<br />\n，老底47，單錢$3，六日假$8<br />\n你問我答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想當年我做果陣得 $30 粒鐘，仲要冇單錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n十年前車手月入8千?"},{"pid":"03dfa9af29e512ba1d28f2d49df8f6ba2afca67a","tid":187742,"uid":54058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T17:51:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>做緊薄餅某傳統公司（果一間）<br />\n，老底47，單錢$3，六日假$8<br />\n你問我答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想當年我做果陣得 $30 粒鐘，仲要冇單錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咩年代，無單錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大約十年前，而家多公司爭人佢先焗住加人工，P沙乞正仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以好多人選擇轉環境 根本連經理級都走佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12b78addef8beb99c59b987f1ebed03e3db23079","tid":187742,"uid":16636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T21:43:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最近多時間想渣下車 等撚左foodpanda 成大半個月 <br />\n先叫我帶齊文件上去 <br />\n袋鼠直情影都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打簽左約上黎講下而家出幾錢<br />\n佢期期唔同好撚狗"},{"pid":"b6540a42f18aae117e45e4814949893f82f33dc5","tid":187742,"uid":24513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T01:42:50.000Z","msg":"你地係咪渣羊<br />\n如果街車會唔會做唔到"},{"pid":"2c92a07a6668dbfbc0980dd91bfe65ad1360b0bb","tid":187742,"uid":54095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T02:57:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你地係咪渣羊<br />\n如果街車會唔會做唔到</blockquote><br />\n多數羊啦 不過而家好多人 尤其係蝻 都鍾意用街車 <br />\n見過有跑車送袋鼠添"},{"pid":"33a19fbf1157723de5653a82e09f8dc5036bdeb9","tid":187742,"uid":50101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T03:34:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>做緊薄餅某傳統公司（果一間）<br />\n，老底47，單錢$3，六日假$8<br />\n你問我答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想當年我做果陣得 $30 粒鐘，仲要冇單錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n十年前車手月入8千?</blockquote><br />\n果陣全職老底連安全獎約 8600，OT 另計時薪$30都冇，聖誕果期先僅僅過萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb2658bc723d60f8f914ff2e3396a450d4e2cf5f","tid":187742,"uid":50101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T03:36:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你地係咪渣羊<br />\n如果街車會唔會做唔到</blockquote><br />\n多數羊啦 不過而家好多人 尤其係蝻 都鍾意用街車 <br />\n見過有跑車送袋鼠添</blockquote><br />\nR6 做袋鼠，不過睇見佢揹住袋個坐姿就辛苦"},{"pid":"61a536d2ffe18112276525a92c7c4be069706429","tid":187742,"uid":54058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite